
#----------------------
# rompp Documentation
#----------------------

THIS IS WORK IN PROGRESS!
This code for ROM uses TriBITS. The project defines a TriBITS CMake project.

To clone this repo, use this command:

   git clone --recursive repo_url

(The recursive option is necessary because it has a git submodule for TriBITS.)


To build ROMPP, clone the auto_build repo:

   git clone --recursive git@gitlab.com:fnrizzi/rompp_auto_build.git

and follows steps in there.
